    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Embark in a breathtaking journey across the Valley, a shattered world that was inhabited a long ago by a mysterious, long gone civilization. You play as a ball of water that's the only hope of saving this land from the forces setting it ablaze. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >    <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3044150/extras/e454e1cdb5fe2373c7ff1019ad03894b.poster.avif?t=1746215770\" width=568 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3044150/extras/e454e1cdb5fe2373c7ff1019ad03894b.webm?t=1746215770\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3044150/extras/e454e1cdb5fe2373c7ff1019ad03894b.mp4?t=1746215770\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Along this journey you will find puzzles that will test your ability to move quickly as you find new and creative ways to solve them.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >    <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3044150/extras/4b4b27d4450a1b02fd99e43735b799bd.poster.avif?t=1746215770\" width=568 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3044150/extras/4b4b27d4450a1b02fd99e43735b799bd.webm?t=1746215770\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3044150/extras/4b4b27d4450a1b02fd99e43735b799bd.mp4?t=1746215770\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Rolling Water is a platformer set in a beautiful natural world with a series of fun and challenging trials set in place by those before you.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >    <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3044150/extras/7d16096c82f89e07c0852448ad740df6.poster.avif?t=1746215770\" width=568 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3044150/extras/7d16096c82f89e07c0852448ad740df6.webm?t=1746215770\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3044150/extras/7d16096c82f89e07c0852448ad740df6.mp4?t=1746215770\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
